cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL 

The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically using recurrent neural networks to classify poems according to their meters. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.DL (Deep Learning). Finally, the crawling and processing of large datasets could also make it relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
